headline: Airbnb Passed, Expedia Pounced: Inside Tiqets’ Long Road to a Sale: Scoop
summary: That Airbnb didn't acquire Tiqets for its own experiences business after leading a Series C funding round, didn't give Tiqets much street cred. The Expedia deal couldn't have been a very substantial one for investors given the lack of financial disclosures.

headline: Airbnb is ’an increasingly attractive brand monetization story’ says RBC
summary: Investing.com -- RBC Capital upgraded Airbnb to Outperform on Wednesday, saying the stock’s extended period out of favor has created a more attractive entry point as the company’s brand and data assets gain importance in a changing consumer landscape.

headline: Airbnb (ABNB) Is Up 5.3% After Analyst Upgrade Highlights Bookings Rebound Amid Spain Fine
summary: In recent weeks, Airbnb has attracted fresh attention after an analyst upgrade highlighted rebounding bookings, stronger free cash flow and a more attractive valuation backdrop, even as Spain imposed a roughly €64–€68 million penalty over unlicensed listings. Alongside this, ongoing insider share sales, regulatory pressures and commentary that Airbnb’s CEO undersells the company’s strengths are shaping how investors weigh its long-term platform potential against legal and governance...
